Name: Initial Access
Intro: The adversary is trying to get into your network.

Name: Execution
Intro: The adversary is trying to run malicious code.

Name: Persistence
Intro: The adversary is trying to maintain their foothold.

Name: Privilege Escalation
Intro: The adversary is trying to gain higher-level permissions.

Name: Defense Evasion
Intro: The adversary is trying to avoid being detected.

Name: Credential Access
Intro: The adversary is trying to steal account names and passwords.

Name: Discovery
Intro: The adversary is trying to figure out your environment.

Name: Lateral Movement
Intro: The adversary is trying to move through your environment.

Name: Collection
Intro: The adversary is trying to gather data of interest to their goal.

Name: Exfiltration
Intro: The adversary is trying to steal data.

Name: Command and Control
Intro: The adversary is trying to communicate with compromised systems to control them.

Name: Impact
Intro: The adversary is trying to manipulate, interrupt, or destroy your systems and data.
